{"tid":2391248,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[Law & Order] 本人正式宣布LIHKG 感情台公審庭三大規條","createTime":"2021-02-02T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:43:31.000Z","uid":78016,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7fae47df386af91895e7d0a0a31335cc91d48d2","tid":2391248,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"前言<br />\n本人追封會員 (小多士) 為感情台永遠榮譽大法官<br />\n雖然多士sir 已被ban 但佢一生對處女嘅追求影響無數後人<br />\n<br />\n最近感情台越來越多人上來公審又唔守規矩<br />\n有見及此 本人公佈感情台公審台 三大規條<br />\n<br />\n1.所有陪審員必須格守無罪假定 (Presumption of innocence) <br />\n即一日未定案 一日都唔可以假定被告有罪<br />\n<br />\n2.無圖無真相 No Photo No Truth<br />\n此規條適用於原告和被告 <br />\n唔好諗住單單打打 post 人相出黎就你岩曬<br />\n&ldquo;要有被人開槍射殺嘅準備 先好開槍殺人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n3.男女平等 不能因為係女講野 就一定係岩曬<br />\n尤其話自己俾人破左處飛左個d 女<br />\nD 人當正佢講乜都係事實 <br />\n呢d 陪審員必須被 Ban<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92ae1f7f242c600b20c5e2f6e25ad41dc9083e2","tid":2391248,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65100273b10375d15d1a7a1c3f6c76d65486458","tid":2391248,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"點解多士仔俾人bam咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ce368644ed5894860a2488dd00e6d41127f202","tid":2391248,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c65100273b10375d15d1a7a1c3f6c76d65486458","tid":2391248,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"點解多士仔俾人bam咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:01:15.000Z","msg":"看破世事"},{"pid":"63e58f18cd9600d5a54f940e4bc71bf282bc4c49","tid":2391248,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/asset